no-nonoctal-decimal-escape.description:
Description

This rule disallows\8and\9escape sequences in string literals.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-nonoctal-decimal-escape: "error"*/

"\8";

"\9";

const foo = "w\8less";

const bar = "December 1\9";

const baz = "Don't use \8 and \9 escapes.";

const quux = "\0\8";

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-nonoctal-decimal-escape: "error"*/

"8";

"9";

const foo = "w8less";

const bar = "December 19";

const baz = "Don't use \\8 and \\9 escapes.";

const quux = "\0\u0038";
